00:02:14.200 --> 00:02:16.557
The apartment empty, a letter on the door:

00:02:16.557 --> 00:02:19.064
“Come back, son. We’re searching for you!

00:02:19.064 --> 00:02:21.280
We reconciled. Don’t want to divorce.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:23.824
Above that, we swear that we will never fight again.

00:02:23.824 --> 00:02:26.262
We have been searching for you for months, day and night.

00:02:26.262 --> 00:02:28.600
We hardly sleep. Our power is draining.”

00:02:28.600 --> 00:02:30.953
Next to it a newspaper article in red:

00:02:30.953 --> 00:02:36.280
“Microsleep. Last night: Married couple dead!”

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:42.865
Enjoy your freedom, son. I will rest in peace from now on.

00:02:42.865 --> 00:02:49.120
I didn’t love your mother. But I always loved you.

